{"tid":2262640,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「有片」地獄鬼國有家具廠員工集體跪地瘋狂自摑　","createTime":"2020-10-29T09:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T21:23:25.000Z","uid":222970,"like":116,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"eca62ef2633f0eb7fc16fef995242106d67eaf6a","tid":2262640,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>片</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4O9o6WsWYTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4O9o6WsWYTg&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kih1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=3b61842a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4O9o6WsWYTg</a><br />\n<br />\n東莞家具廠員工集體跪地自摑　廠方辯稱「激發最巔峰狀態」惹議<br />\n<br />\n撰文：彭琤琳<br />\n2020-10-29 15:14<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-10-29 15:53<br />\n<br />\n近日，一段廣東東莞家具廠員工集體跪地自摑的短片在網上流傳。片中顯示，眾人跪地自扇耳光，更有人脫去上衣一邊叫口號一邊雙手拍地，情緒激動。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的家具廠華南區品牌經理張先生表示，上述影片來自一場培訓，是為了「讓員工們激發最巔峰的狀態」。惟事件引起極大爭議，有網民稱「這不是巔峰，是瘋癲」。<br />\n<br />\n合內媒報道，事發在10月20日，東莞一間家具廠的營銷事業部門組織了一場導購員「心靈成長」培訓，參與學員來自全國各地終端銷售員，屬於自願報名、自願參與。經理張先生稱，類似培訓大概一年一次。「此次培訓為了打造鐵軍團，讓員工們激發最巔峰的狀態，培訓完之後員工的狀態都非常好。」<br />\n<br />\n網傳的影片顯示，多名身穿制服的員工集體跪地，大聲叫口號，情緒激動。其中有人自扇耳光，脫下衣服，跪在地上用手拍打地面。員工面前坐有另一排身穿統一服飾的人，不斷抬手示意。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起關注後，東莞市人力資源與社會保障局辦公室的工作人員表示，目前市人社局已介入對該事件的調查。涉事公司則通過官方微信公眾號發布聲明稱，對影片中的過激行為以及對社會造成的不良影響深表歉意，會深刻反省並對以後的所有培訓課程嚴格審查，還會對相關責任人進行嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n有內地律師表示，從員工與企業之間的關係上看，相關爭議行為在一定程度上有違公序良俗，在民事勞動關係中，員工有權拒絕參加單位這種培訓活動。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）"},{"pid":"26ab30e94d6743cc54ae48eabcfb6807dd856ace","tid":2262640,"uid":222970,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbBHi7j.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbbBHi7j.gif&h=a92afe16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yM3RWUg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM3RWUg.gif&h=78b238fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9769849ae35164d8cedc9ea0b3d9c94dcc124ed2","tid":2262640,"uid":78243,"like":55,"dislike":6,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"自摑師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bbe5ad2ef8a9141548b18a20b424018ce6a004","tid":2262640,"uid":52215,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"d女除埋衫自摸咪正囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc273f4fd3b4d7f4d1f552c094a0f3a98f9164c1","tid":2262640,"uid":239056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"打到七情上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72f05041eef92844750943ab4a0bfbea58e3788","tid":2262640,"uid":77196,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"邪教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32089d2937e4c690001c8aeafe87f7520e85ee12","tid":2262640,"uid":31389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"35dcb4248199a510ce31cd849f88e92416c58646","tid":2262640,"uid":39796,"like":119,"dislike":0,"score":119,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"博盡無悔"},{"pid":"0704ea74750e1caf474f2287af1aa0c85396c46b","tid":2262640,"uid":29423,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"b7bbe5ad2ef8a9141548b18a20b424018ce6a004","tid":2262640,"uid":52215,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"d女除埋衫自摸咪正囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"廠長激發廠妹懷孕狀態"},{"pid":"8d3c6fc211db4d2370d8199bbb3f28e063bcbb9f","tid":2262640,"uid":31215,"like":188,"dis